A class named 'laMiaSocket' is provided with functions of:
1. new a object with its type(server or client), port
2. send message to which ip(using sendMessage(ip), default is to local machine of "127.0.0.1")
3. recieve message from which ip(using recvMessage(ip), default is from local machine)
4. this class is fine to use both under windows or linux
5. details of usage can be found in socket.cc
6. to be continue...


Usage:
  make clean
  make all
  ./socket
















